          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1658224748367-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>chopped garlic</strong> (don't like raw garlic? Go easy!), <strong>chopped spinach</strong>, most of the <strong>chopped basil</strong> (save some for garnish!) and <strong>chopped mint</strong> to a <strong>food processor</strong></p><p>Add 2 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tbsp]</span> <strong>olive oil</strong>, a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and a grind of <strong>black pepper</strong> and blitz until smooth</p><p>Add the <strong>chicken stock mix</strong>, <strong>soft cheese </strong>and 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp] </span><strong>cold water </strong>and blitz again – this is your <strong>mint & basil pesto</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
