    {
      "instruction": "<p>Top, tail and peel lengths off the<strong> courgette<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> with a peeler until you end up with a pile of <strong>courgette ribbons</strong></p><p>Chop the<strong> remaining</strong> <strong>courgette core<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span> </strong>into bite-sized pieces</p>",
      "order": 4,
