    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>bacon lardons</strong> and cook for 3-4 min or until golden and crisp</p><p>Once golden, add the <strong>chopped courgette core</strong> to the pan and cook for 2 min further or until softened and caramelised</p>",
